        "created_at": "2024-12-15T05:59:33.276Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The current behavior of the search inside a conversation is confusing and badly designed. Users don’t understand it. The search button should open a text input inside the conversation, not just slightly change the appearance of the search input in the list of contacts.</p>\n<p>Contextually, you are in the right side of the UI, which is about the current conversation. Switching to the left pane, which is for the list of conversations, is not a good idea.</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-257286-steps-to-reproduce-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-257286-steps-to-reproduce-1\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>Steps to reproduce</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>click on search button above conversation with contact</li>\n<li>nothing happens</li>\n<li>re-click on search button</li>\n<li>nothing happens</li>\n<li>re-re-click on search</li>\n<li>actually notice that the text focus has moved out of the message textarea to the search text input inside the contacts list</li>\n</ol>\n<h3><a name=\"p-257286-expected-result-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-257286-expected-result-2\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>Expected result</h3>\n<p>the search button inside a specific conversation should open a search input inside the conversation</p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-257286-actual-result-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-257286-actual-result-3\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>Actual result</h3>\n<p>the search button focuses on the input text for searching in all messages</p>\n<p>Before clicking on button:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/7/d/7dea5bb3d58d977c664cef945ae358da197a9e42.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/7dea5bb3d58d977c664cef945ae358da197a9e42\" title=\"\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/7/d/7dea5bb3d58d977c664cef945ae358da197a9e42_2_690x398.png\" alt=\"\" data-base62-sha1=\"hXTNdZdIyedtP88FW74Sv0PwpF0\" width=\"690\" height=\"398\" role=\"presentation\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/7/d/7dea5bb3d58d977c664cef945ae358da197a9e42_2_690x398.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/7/d/7dea5bb3d58d977c664cef945ae358da197a9e42_2_1035x597.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/7/d/7dea5bb3d58d977c664cef945ae358da197a9e42_2_1380x796.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"DFE6F3\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\"></span><span class=\"informations\">1918×1108 48.7 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>After clicking on button:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/0/9/09a56a7778091b79d4902ef6825573f7334d7b64.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/09a56a7778091b79d4902ef6825573f7334d7b64\" title=\"\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/9/09a56a7778091b79d4902ef6825573f7334d7b64_2_690x385.png\" alt=\"\" data-base62-sha1=\"1nkHlteTkBbBGSYFjAL4WA0utN2\" width=\"690\" height=\"385\" role=\"presentation\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/9/09a56a7778091b79d4902ef6825573f7334d7b64_2_690x385.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/9/09a56a7778091b79d4902ef6825573f7334d7b64_2_1035x577.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/0/9/09a56a7778091b79d4902ef6825573f7334d7b64_2_1380x770.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"DEE5F3\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\"></span><span class=\"informations\">1918×1071 43.3 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
